      CUMCQACDRSBUQCBCQCGGEUPGNEHCQCGUOACGDTUAUBUCUDUSELZVAVDVCURVEUTUMUNUSEDUE
      UFVEABVBUQFUSEUPUGUHUIACDUJUKUL $.
      $([28-Mar-97]$)
  $}

  ${
    $d x y A $.  $d y ph $.  $( ` y ` is dummy. $)
    $( A restricted abstraction of a wff with restricted existential
       uniqueness exists belongs to the restriction.  Useful for proving
       closure laws for definitions in theories about restricted classes. $)
    reucl $p |- ( E! x e. A ph -> U. { x e. A | ph } e. A ) $=
      ( vy cv wcel wa weu cab cuni wreu crab csn wceq wex eusn wel wal hbe1
